      title: 'Louisiana Birthday Rule: How It Helps You Change Medigap Plans',
      excerpt: 'Louisiana\'s Birthday Rule is a valuable consumer protection that allows Medicare beneficiaries to change Medigap plans annually during their birthday month without health questions or penalties. Learn how this rule works and how to use it to find better coverage or lower premiums.',
